metadata.name: Iyawo  Shao
metadata.description: The undaunted Shao Bride, one of the brides that got married at the recent Shao Awon Mass Wedding festival. In the picture above, the clothing materials she is putting on is called 'Aso Oke' which was originated in the Southwestern part of Nigeria in the 15th century by the Yorubas that shows Pride and Honour.
